How do you think that went over?

630
00:28:40,900 --> 00:28:42,100
Why don't you tell me?

631
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,800
The one night that ruined my life

632
00:28:43,900 --> 00:28:49,000
Gave him everything-Grace-

