638
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:12,300
I know what i did on that road,

639
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:14,500
But i didn't do this.

640
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:16,800
I didn't kill myself.

641
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:19,000
I wasn't a drug addict.

642
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:21,500
Whose life do you think would be a lot better

643
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:23,700
With me gone?

644
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:26,400
Are you saying ryan killed you?

645
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,300
I'm dead,aren't i?

646
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:46,500
Eli.

647
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:49,400
I know how ryan killed his friend.

648
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:50,700
Now we know that lucas was on

649
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:53,400
Some pretty hefty happy pills.

