00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:40,300
Let's go.

672
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:42,600
Why? Just...

673
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:45,500
And i think in his own way

674
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:47,900
He loved every single person here,

675
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:51,200
And what i think that he would want the most

676
00:30:51,300 --> 00:30:53,200
Is for all of us to move forward,

677
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:55,600
To find the things that he was still searching for

678
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:57,800
With the people that we love.

679
00:30:57,900 --> 00:31:00,400
Grace and i are doing that.

680
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:02,000
We're getting married.

681
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,300
And when i say that we lost our best man,

682
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,600
I mean it in every sense of the word.

683
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:15,400
We all did.

684
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,400
To lucas.

685
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:19,600
To lucas! To lucas!

686
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:20,900
Want to do something,

687
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,400
Or should i?

688
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,700
We should go outside and talk.

689
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:30,600
Look. I know what grace told you,

690
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:32,600
And there's a statute of limitations,

691
