00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:10,900
Ah,no.

709
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:12,500
Grace,wait!

710
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:16,000
You think you're the only person that cared about him?

711
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:18,100
He was my best friend.

712
00:32:18,100 --> 00:32:19,400
I was just trying to make things ok.

713
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:22,100
