00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:42,000
He's here,isn't he?

724
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:52,900
Since seventh grade, we were best friends.

725
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,200
On the first day of high school,

726
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:58,500
