00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:26,300
Who was that?

733
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,000
Here you go,lucas.

734
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,700
Thanks,man.

735
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:36,000
Later,i tried to act like nothing happened,

736
00:33:36,100 --> 00:33:37,900
And i realized that we all were

737
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:40,600
And that lucas knew and that's why he was drinking.

738
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:41,900
It wasn't like him.

739
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:52,200
It was our fault. We did this to him.

740
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:54,100
Leaving that guy on the road,

741
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,500
I wasn't just protecting myself.

742
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:59,400
I was protecting all of us,

743
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:01,400
And when my best friend came to me,

744
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:04,400
Falling apart after 10 years,

745
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,800
I just tried to do the same thing.

746
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:08,300
I tried to save him...

747
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:10,700
Or at least,that's what i thought i was doing.

748
00:34:10,700 --> 00:34:13,400
I didn't come asking for permission this time.

749
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:17,500
Ryan,a man died because i was drinking,

750
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:20,000
Because we left him there like he was some kind of animal.

751
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,400
Ahh,ahh.

752
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:23,200
Because i told you to.

753
00:34:23,300 --> 00:34:24,500
Look. The guy was gone.

754
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:25,800
There was nothing we could do.

755
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,500
