764
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,500
You still seeing your shrink?

765
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:51,400
I'm done with all that.

766
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:54,300
Whatever decision you make,i'm behind you,

767
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:57,300
