768
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,700
Look. You said you haven't been sleeping.

769
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,700
I'm gonna give you something,ok? Yeah.

770
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:03,900
You just take a couple of days.

771
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,200
Do that for me, all right?

772
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:08,500
Yeah.

773
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:12,100
I told him don't mix those pills with anything.

774
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:13,600
I swear,

