781
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:37,200
Late at night every night.

782
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:38,700
I hadn't slept for so long.

783
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:41,300
The pills my shrink had prescribed to me,

784
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:43,100
They weren't helping, they didn't do anything,

785
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:46,800
So what harm could a sleeping pill do?

786
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:48,400
I woke up again.

787
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:50,500
It had to have been hours since i took the first one.

788
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:52,900
Why wasn't i sleeping?

789
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:07,700
I went out to my car to get headphones.

790
00:36:07,700 --> 00:36:09,100
I had neighbors,

791
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:11,300
And next thing i know...

792
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:17,500
I'm standing over my own body.

793
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:20,700
I saw grace. She looked so sad,

794
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:23,500
Even before she found me.

795
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:25,200
I needed to make them understand.

796
00:36:25,300 --> 00:36:30,600
The sadness,it just doesn't go away.

797
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,300
Lucas may not have realized it,

798
00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:34,400
But i think he was trying to save you.

799
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,800
From what?

800
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:39,900
From making the same mistake he did.

801
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,700
He was afraid that if you kept

802
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:45,200
Your guilt a secret it would ruin your life

803
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:47,500
The way that it ruined his.

804
00:36:47,600 --> 00:36:51,100
Lucas,i'm sorry.

805
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:55,700
We are both so sorry.

806
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:59,700
I didn't see it coming.

807
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:03,900
My girlfriend, my best friend.

