00:37:17,700 --> 00:37:21,400
You're asking me?

812
00:37:21,500 --> 00:37:23,900
What a difference 10 years makes.

813
00:37:31,500 --> 00:37:35,100
What i see now is that it was an accident-

814
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:37,700
The crash,your death, all of it.

815
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:41,000
You made a mistake.

816
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,300
It's time for you to move on

817
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:45,900
And let your friends do the same.

818
00:37:56,800 --> 00:38:00,400
Mrs. Graber,these are the two people i told you about.

